Name: Add recipe
Actors: Users with accounts
Goals: Add a recipe to the database storing all recipes
Preconditions: User must have an account
Summary: User creates a new recipe and saves it into the recipe database
Related use case: Edit Recipe, Delete Recipe
Steps: Actors - System Response
1. Requests to add new recipe
2. Asks for the recipe name/class/type/category/ingredients/directions
3. Provides the required information
4. Prompt the selection of confirmation/ canceling
5. Choose confirm or cancel to save the new recipe
6. Confirmation of the addition/clear of the new recipe
Postconditions: The new recipe created by the user is accessible by all other users


